            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/freepik__background__68644_1.png",
            "accordion_title": "Transparency",
            "accordion_content": "<p>We share openly how our food is grown, sourced, and prepared, because knowing what you eat, and where it comes from, is essential to real nourishment and trust.<br/><br/></p>"
