            "accordion_title": "Nourishment with Purpose",
            "accordion_content": "<p>Our foods are designed to deliver real benefits through functional, whole-food nutrition: complete plant protein, naturally occurring fiber, and sustained energy, using an ancestral crop that has nourished Andean communities for centuries.</p>"
